{"tid":14440,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"坤 哥 結 婚 會 公 開","createTime":"2016-11-30T13:28:12.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-02T10:45:13.000Z","uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"13eb8739ee32c2830cdb61df021185de002d58dc","tid":14440,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T13:28:12.000Z","msg":"吳業坤昨日在商台宣傳新推出大碟，他指今年已做想做的事，例如紅館開個唱及出大碟，笑說：「人生出到一次大碟真係死而無憾，做咗咁多想做嘅嘢，夠鐘死心。」 <br />\n<br />\n至於周柏豪日前結婚，坤哥感意外，他說：「覺得係幸褔美滿嘅故事，郎才女貌。」而他感對方不公開，可能怕刺激歌迷，很體貼細心，而自己將來結婚則會公開。"},{"pid":"c9179451e31a685b4c35cc5ed3c4019af680d903","tid":14440,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T13:29:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20161130/large/30ec3p8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20161130%2Flarge%2F30ec3p8.jpg&h=1fc759c6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"253c4fb372eca4f38addd929ebacb58de274485d","tid":14440,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T13:29:38.000Z","msg":"點貼圖呀屌!"},{"pid":"607134f40b2a332ef26e5dc1c89c009ebe82b7e6","tid":14440,"uid":25373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T13:33:17.000Z","msg":"冇人想知呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"283a880adf9ea3cbba1bd00a84c8ef6b862c3687","tid":14440,"uid":25373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T13:34:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點貼圖呀屌!</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/30/213450_49310f799999b0aad3e18ea385986bda.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F30%2F213450_49310f799999b0aad3e18ea385986bda.jpg&h=e0f428d5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ff905fa7c76a47f08ddb3596ba37a67baf07d871","tid":14440,"uid":35301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime